very healthy the way it is connected there.
Who do I suspect on that level? That's probably

00:00:39.750 --> 00:00:45.000
slugs. What can you do to keep slugs away?
A good way to keep them out is Diatomaceous

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:49.350
earth it is a product that you can find in
any pull supply store and often in a lot of

00:00:49.350 --> 00:00:55.160
good garden centers. It is all natural, it
adds calcium to your soil and slugs hate it

00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:59.320
they won't cross it. Just put a little thin
ring of Diatomaceous earth around your plant

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:05.930
that would help it keep it away from it. The
