00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:37.590
animal on the insect side that is eating this
if I get the right BT and you do have to ask

00:01:37.590 --> 00:01:41.520
the people in your garden center when you
are buying the BT. You don't want the stuff

00:01:41.520 --> 00:01:45.840
called israelensis. That is for mosquitoes.
